        <item>
            <title>今年 8 月世锦赛发表，手机游戏《Pokémon TCG Pocket》正式推出</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/pokemon-tcg-pocket-now-available/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=pokemon-tcg-pocket-now-available</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/pokemon-tcg-pocket-now-available/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 02:00:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokémon TCG Pocket]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1272333</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在今年 8 月举行的宝可梦世界锦标赛（Pokémon World Championships）期间，手机游戏《Pokémon TCG Pocket》发表。经过接近两个月的等待，宝可梦粉丝们终于可以玩到这款简化版宝可梦换卡游戏（Pokémon Trading Card）的手机版本。游戏在 8 月公布后已经开放预先注册，玩家现在可以下载游戏和游玩。</p><p><span id="more-1272333"></span></p><p>《Pokémon TCG Pocket》将宝可梦换卡游戏的玩法简化，不像另一游戏《Pokémon TCG Live》般深入和复杂，因此玩家可以随时随地轻松游玩。《Pokémon TCG Pocket》的玩法与实体版卡牌游戏接近，玩家可以每日免费开启两包虚拟增强包组建卡牌组，亦可课金购买额外卡牌包或高级对战通行证，去解锁更多数码内容。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_88251"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2rNXBt4go_g?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>游戏内设有基础教学，玩家需要完成和达到等级 3 才能够解锁「Battling」模式，并可透过「Versus」模式与其他玩家对战或挑战电脑对手。Pokémon Company 有详尽入门指南，帮助从未玩过这卡牌游戏的新手尽快掌握。</p><p><strong>Pokémon TCG Pocket</strong><br />
下载：<a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6479970832?mt=8">iOS</a> / <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.pokemon.pokemontcgp">Android</a><br />
售价：免费</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/31/pokemon-tcg-pocket-now-available/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
